@jonasschnelli 

> I'm unsure about the locale dependent formatting. What would you recommend instead of `itotsr`?

I recommend `ToString()` (`util/string.h`) :)

ACK 222d5334681c517636c933c9491200fbbabf3c8d code review, built/ran tests, fuzzed for 24 hours as described in https://github.com/bitcoin/bitcoin/pull/18242#issuecomment-626172638. Could squash the 2 fix commits into their parents, happy to re-ACK in that case. There will be follow-ups as described in the PR description and from the review and BIP feedback, possibly also related to [MACing the length](https://gist.github.com/jonasschnelli/c530ea8421b8d0e80c51486325587c52#gistcomment-3297213); the changes here are only used in the added tests and I think it can be merged.

